      "acceptanceCriteria": "SQA level 2 requires documented version control, issue tracking, and regression test suite covering primary load cases. Achieved by Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1 with ANSYS QA documentation package and DePuy Synthes internal SQA records on file.",
      "rationale": "Commercial FEA solver (Ansys Mechanical 2022 R1) used with vendor-supplied quality documentation. DePuy Synthes internal SQA records confirm version-controlled input decks and regression testing against benchmark problems. Gradation 2 achieved."
